flowchart TD
    cmd["bash 命令\n（可能是管道）"]
    split["分割为命令部分\n（处理 &&/||/|/;）"]
    neutral{是 SEMANTIC_NEUTRAL\n命令?}
    skip["跳过\n（中性命令不影响分类）"]
    known{在四个集合里?}
    classify["标记 isSearch/isRead/isList"]
    unknown["立即返回全 false\n（整个管道视为修改）"]
    result["合并结果\n返回 isSearch/isRead/isList"]

    cmd --> split
    split --> neutral
    neutral -->|是| skip
    neutral -->|否| known
    known -->|否| unknown
    known -->|是| classify
    classify --> result
    skip --> result
